all_steps.description: Picked up the car and drove to Meteora. What a magical place. Visiting the monasteries tomorrow.

What an amazing place; six 14th century Monasteries on top of giant cliffs (that were built to fight off Turkish invasion). We had clear skies and a pretty epic sunset to finish off the day. Moving on to Istanbul tmr.
First full day in Istanbul. A bit hung over we strolled through the city. We visited the Blue Mosque, wandered around Sultan Ahmed and enjoyed the evening views over the Bosphorus.
